
 React Router (Pages & Navigation)
📘 What is React Router?
React Router is a standard library for routing in React. It enables navigation between views/components in a React app — just like pages in a website — without refreshing the browser.

🔧 Step-by-Step Setup
1. Install React Router
In your React app folder:

bash
Copy
Edit
npm install react-router-dom
